---
title: Lemon Pepper Beef Rissoles & Veggie Brown Rice with Garlic Yoghurt
description: Brown rice becomes irresistible when there’s a helping of beef rissoles on top. These rissoles will surprise you with a buffet of
flavours, from zest to pepper from our special seasoning, to a smokey-sweet combo of onion chutney. Finishing it off tonight is
a fragrant garlic yoghurt dolloped on top.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

